---
description: Source-of-truth rules for the signtraker API client project.
globs:
alwaysApply: true
---
Before implementing or changing API behavior, read
`docs/planning/signtraker-api-client/foundation/api-source-of-truth.md` and
`docs/planning/signtraker-api-client/foundation/source-of-truth-matrix.md`.

Prefer sources in this order:
1. explicit API docs URL from the user (https://theperrygroup.signtraker.com/api-docs)
2. checked-in `docs/api/`
3. checked-in OpenAPI or Swagger artifacts
4. endpoint task docs or backlog notes

If the sources disagree, record the contradiction in the planning tree before
coding. The SignTraker host is tenant-specific; never hardcode a single tenant
as the default base URL.
